1
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:33,660
[Governor's Secret Love]
[Episode 11]

2
00:00:35,960 --> 00:00:37,480
Please get up, General Hu.

3
00:00:38,800 --> 00:00:42,040
Your Majesty, Xueqing is the blue blood.

4
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,520
How dare a eunuch threaten her.

5
00:00:43,920 --> 00:00:45,120
If you disagree with this,

6
00:00:45,200 --> 00:00:46,800
I'll be held accountable

7
00:00:46,800 --> 00:00:48,560
when the Duke of Defender returns.

8
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:51,000
I'd rather take my life

9
00:00:51,240 --> 00:00:54,440
before your witness.

10
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,560
General Hu.

11
00:00:58,160 --> 00:00:59,520
Are you threatening me?

12
00:01:00,760 --> 00:01:01,400
Your Majesty,

13
00:01:02,440 --> 00:01:04,280
punish me if you like.

14
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:10,720
By the edict of His Majesty,

15
00:01:11,080 --> 00:01:13,400
you defied and abducted
Princess Xueqing.

16
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,000
This is a humiliating

17
00:01:15,160 --> 00:01:16,080
and rebellious act
to the imperial family.

18
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:19,040
Due to your dedicated service,
you'll be granted a dignified death.

19
00:01:19,440 --> 00:01:22,160
The execution will be carried out
in seven days. That's all.

20
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:25,040
Come with us, Eunuch Fugui.

21
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,200
This is nonsense!

22
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:28,040
Xueqing started the row first.

23
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,440
You can't take Fugui with you.

24
00:01:30,080 --> 00:01:32,040
Insolent! Do you intend
to defy the imperial edict?

25
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:34,280
I dare not. But I'm desperate now.

26
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,840
I accept the charge.

27
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:46,080
Fugui, tell them

28
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:46,880
the truth.

29
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:47,760
You threatened Princess Xueqing

30
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:48,840
because you wanted to save me.

31
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:49,760
Tell the truth now.

32
00:01:50,240 --> 00:01:51,040
Jixiang.

33
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:53,520
Chief Eunuch saved my life before.

34
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:54,800
From now on,

35
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:57,160
please take care of him on my behalf.

36
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:04,720
We should leave now.

37
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,200
Come on.

38
00:02:08,920 --> 00:02:09,520
Chief Eunuch.

39
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:13,880
You can't let them take Fugui away.

40
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:21,560
Fugui!

41
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:22,440
Jixiang.

42
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,080
Stop.

43
00:02:35,120 --> 00:02:36,800
The Duke of Defender is returning soon.

44
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,000
I planned to make Princess Xueqing

45
00:02:39,000 --> 00:02:39,640
to break off the engagement

46
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,480
and send you to the prison

47
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,840
as to cover your movement

48
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:45,120
when you gather evidence
to bring General Hu down.

49
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,280
But the plan went south.

50
00:02:47,920 --> 00:02:48,920
You're meticulous.

51
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,800
Jixiang was eager to save me

52
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,320
so she ruined the plan.

53
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,760
Please don't blame her, Your Majesty.

54
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:57,320
I can't believe
you'd plead for a servant.

55
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,880
I'm getting more curious

56
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,760
about Jixiang.

57
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,200
She's a soothsayer.

58
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:05,800
She saved my life several times.

59
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,120
She told me about that before.

60
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:12,640
At this rate, what's your next step?

61
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,720
I've already investigated
the ledgers and witnesses

62
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,520
for the embezzlement of military
and relief funds done by General Hu.

63
00:03:18,640 --> 00:03:19,720
I hid it in the Longevity Shrine.

64
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,240
All we need to do now

65
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,640
is ask Fugui to bring them back.

66
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,760
Fugui?

67
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,480
Do you mean we should stick to the plan?

68
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:27,920
Eunuch Fugui will execute the plan.

69
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,400
He's my trusted aide.
We can rely on him.

70
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,040
In the coming days,
I'll pretend to leave the capital

71
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,160
to keep Fugui's tracks covered.

72
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:37,160
Even if we find the evidence,

73
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,320
Eunuch Fugui still can't escape
the death sentence.

74
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,560
With the Duke of Defender on his side,

75
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,800
General Hu is unlikely

76
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,720
to acknowledge
the testimony and ledgers.

77
00:03:46,640 --> 00:03:47,080
No.

78
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:50,000
I will trade these ledgers to General Hu

79
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,280
for Fugui's safety.

80
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,920
What do you mean?

81
00:03:53,320 --> 00:03:54,440
We have been waiting in the wings

82
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:55,840
to take revenge against them,
haven't we?

83
00:03:56,160 --> 00:03:57,680
If you were to hand over
the evidence to General Hu,

84
00:03:57,880 --> 00:03:58,840
how about our revenge?

85
00:03:59,000 --> 00:03:59,760
Be patient, Your Majesty.

86
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:02,240
As you said,

87
00:04:02,320 --> 00:04:03,400
General Hu is unlikely to own up

88
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,040
even if we've found
solid evidence of their doings.

89
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:08,240
On that note,
why don't we use this chance

90
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,560
to lower his guard against us?

91
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:11,040
General Hu

92
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,480
passes himself off as a tough man,

93
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,920
but in fact, he's a coward.

94
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,880
Who knows, he might be of use to us.

95
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:18,920
What's our next step, then?

96
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,240
What if

97
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,400
we have the petition from the people?

98
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,320
Chief Eunuch.

99
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,560
Chief Eunuch.

100
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,160
What's the matter?

101
00:04:36,960 --> 00:04:39,000
Fugui has been serving you
all this time.

102
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,400
Why are you leaving for duty

103
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,800
at a critical moment like this?

104
00:04:41,960 --> 00:04:43,720
Do you have no sympathy?

105
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:47,760
Sympathy?

106
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,920
What makes you think I have sympathy?

107
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,440
Fine.

108
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,720
Be that as it may,

109
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,440
I'm the reason
for his current situation.

110
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:58,440
Could you tell His Majesty

111
00:04:58,600 --> 00:04:59,480
that I want to trade my life

112
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,600
for Fugui's freedom?

113
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:02,760
Jixiang.

114
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,720
Does the bond

115
00:05:05,880 --> 00:05:07,760
between you and Eunuch Fugui
grow so deep

116
00:05:08,640 --> 00:05:10,320
in just a few days?

117
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,280
All I know is

118
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:17,800
one should have sympathy and reasons.

119
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,760
We serve the same master here.

120
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,000
Besides, he's condemned to execution

121
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,200
because of me.

122
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:24,720
I must save him for whatever reason.

123
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,680
He always teases me,

124
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:30,600
