to do with this.

125
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:33,040
For whatever reason?

126
00:05:33,680 --> 00:05:35,120
What a sound logic you have.

127
00:05:36,960 --> 00:05:38,040
Mind you,

128
00:05:38,040 --> 00:05:39,680
