the frigging Hu has sympathy

129
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,640
and Princess Xueqing has reasons?

130
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:47,280
Many people in this world have died

131
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,480
without knowing why.

132
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,960
Do you think
they are just random tragedies?

133
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:56,640
To deal with this riff-raff,

134
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,640
your compassion

135
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:03,660
♪Is a poignant love♪

136
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:06,200
♪First encounter, last farewell♪

137
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,560
and whining

138
00:06:09,400 --> 00:06:11,400
are no use.

139
00:06:13,180 --> 00:06:15,300
♪Who is my obsession?♪

140
00:06:15,300 --> 00:06:19,060
♪Only red plums and white snow know♪

141
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:23,780
♪The most predictable thing♪

142
00:06:23,780 --> 00:06:26,360
