after getting drunk♪

143
00:06:26,360 --> 00:06:27,160
Don't you forget this.

144
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,400
You're just a servant here.

145
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:33,440
You're in no place
to tell me what to do.

146
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:36,120
I didn't mean that.

147
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:39,280
I'm just begging you to save Fugui.

148
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,440
He's my servant.

149
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:44,680
Not your friend.

150
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,320
He saved you because I ordered him so.

151
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:50,440
Also,

152
00:06:55,440 --> 00:06:56,480
don't

153
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,960
point your finger at me.

154
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,240
Murong Cang.

155
00:07:14,080 --> 00:07:14,880
Jixiang.

156
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,080
Jixiang.

157
00:07:16,080 --> 00:07:17,280
What happened? What's the hurry?

158
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,520
Something bad has happened!

159
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,040
I got news from the palace.

160
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,240
Eunuch Fugui

161
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,200
will be executed tomorrow.

162
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,760
How could that be?
It's supposed to be seven days later.

163
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,440
I have no idea.

164
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:34,640
Little brat, you'll come to me.

165
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,480
It must be her.

166
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:40,480
I prepared this for Fugui.

167
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,520
Please send this to him.

168
00:07:42,200 --> 00:07:42,760
Jixiang.

169
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:44,720
Jixiang, where are you going?

170
00:07:45,140 --> 00:07:48,340
(Duke of Defender's Mansion)

171
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,160
Your Highness.

172
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,200
Your Highness.

173
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,800
Your Highness.

174
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,000
Open the door.

175
00:07:57,520 --> 00:07:58,360
Your Highness.

176
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,720
Your Highness.

177
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,920
Princess Xueqing.

178
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:06,880
Your Highness.

179
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,640
Please open the door.

180
00:08:19,880 --> 00:08:21,880
I know you'll come here.

181
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:26,120
But you're later than I expected.

182
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,720
It's getting dark.

183
00:08:28,920 --> 00:08:30,240
I should rest up now.

184
00:08:30,640 --> 00:08:31,680
Please leave.

185
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:34,600
Your Highness.

186
00:08:41,800 --> 00:08:43,360
Chief Eunuch's favorite

187
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,920
is kneeling at my door.

188
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,560
People might misunderstand me

189
00:08:46,560 --> 00:08:48,000
for having a beef

190
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:49,280
with Chief Eunuch.

191
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:50,440
Come in.

192
00:08:54,540 --> 00:09:02,940
(Duke of Defender's Mansion)

193
00:09:12,640 --> 00:09:13,440
Your Highness.

194
00:09:14,720 --> 00:09:16,320
I'm your target.

195
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,600
So here I am.

196
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,440
Please release Fugui.

197
00:09:22,040 --> 00:09:24,000
