from you, though.

198
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,200
Anyway,

199
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,200
it's good.

200
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,960
Murong Cang will lose
his interest in you.

201
00:09:33,680 --> 00:09:35,000
This is a misunderstanding.

202
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:35,840
Chief Eunuch

203
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:37,680
is my godfather.

204
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,160
Misunderstanding, you say?

205
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:42,720
Why?

206
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,440
Do you mean

207
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,560
you don't like Murong Cang?

208
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,400
Your Highness.

209
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,120
I beg of you.

210
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,160
Please release Fugui.

211
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,080
I might consider that.

212
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,360
To be honest,

213
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:17,120
I'm averse to blood.

214
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:19,520
However,

215
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:21,000
my life is too boring.

216
00:10:21,120 --> 00:10:22,920
You won't understand this, anyway.

217
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:32,240
Are you saying
that you agree to release him?

218
00:10:32,680 --> 00:10:33,560
I always know

219
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,160
you're beautiful and kind.

220
00:10:35,440 --> 00:10:37,440
You're blessed with great fortune.

221
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:38,960
How about this?

222
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:41,640
Let's play a game.

223
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,040
I'll give you two options.

224
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,520
The first option,

225
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,760
I'll give you some money.

226
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:51,680
Go anywhere you want

227
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,560
and never appear

228
00:10:53,560 --> 00:10:55,160
before Murong Cang.

229
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:56,880
The second option...

230
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,560
I'll take the second option.

231
00:11:01,840 --> 00:11:03,480
The second option is

232
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:06,360
to go to the back garden and kneel.

233
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:08,120
The longer you kneel,

234
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:11,480
the later I'll postpone his execution.
How does that sound?

235
00:11:12,160 --> 00:11:12,840
I'll do it.

236
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:15,640
You didn't hesitate.

237
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:17,320
No second thoughts?

238
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,680
No. Thank you, Your Highness.

239
00:11:23,640 --> 00:11:24,120
Very good.

240
00:11:25,280 --> 00:11:26,720
In that case,

241
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,880
