00:14:03,980 --> 00:14:06,500
♪Please grant me a good end♪

281
00:14:06,500 --> 00:14:09,500
♪Even though our good times
might scatter at any time♪

282
00:14:09,500 --> 00:14:12,780
♪Or we embraced
in fear of losing each other♪

283
00:14:12,780 --> 00:14:16,500
♪We fall so deeply for each other,
and we shall never forget♪

284
00:14:17,760 --> 00:14:19,280
Your Majesty, great news!

285
00:14:19,440 --> 00:14:22,280
Chief Eunuch's plan succeeded.

286
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:25,600
Chief Eunuch.

287
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:28,120
I might get beaten again

288
00:14:28,200 --> 00:14:29,480
when I come in later.

289
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:30,840
Can you please spare me

290
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,840
from the spanking?

291
00:14:31,840 --> 00:14:32,880
Cut your nonsense.

292
00:14:33,160 --> 00:14:35,000
Keep your mouth shut,
or I'll send you here again.

293
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:35,600
No, please.

294
00:14:35,600 --> 00:14:36,320
Wait for your execution here.

295
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:39,320
I miss you so much when I'm here.

296
00:14:40,320 --> 00:14:41,400
Why didn't Jixiang, that brat, come?

297
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,560
I'm sorry.

298
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,560
I'm to blame.

299
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:49,720
Where is Jixiang?

300
00:14:50,880 --> 00:14:52,480
On the day you left,

301
00:14:52,480 --> 00:14:54,160
we received word from General Hu

302
00:14:54,160 --> 00:14:56,040
that Eunuch Fugui
would be executed immediately.

303
00:14:56,880 --> 00:14:58,760
Jixiang...

304
00:14:58,760 --> 00:14:59,480
Fire away.

305
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,480
She went to see Princess Xueqing.

306
00:15:04,880 --> 00:15:05,720
- Chief Eunuch.
- Chief Eunuch.

307
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:09,440
He doesn't care about me anymore.

308
00:15:09,640 --> 00:15:10,040
Chief Eunuch.

309
00:15:14,260 --> 00:15:18,980
♪Wind and rain escape grasp♪

310
00:15:20,460 --> 00:15:25,140
♪The enticing illusion feels elusive♪

311
00:15:25,860 --> 00:15:28,900
♪Two clouds chance upon each other♪

312
00:15:29,220 --> 00:15:32,020
♪Yet fall out as snow eventually♪

313
00:15:32,340 --> 00:15:37,980
♪They drift down upon past memories♪

314
00:15:38,980 --> 00:15:43,980
♪I blame the limited time
for limitless love♪

315
00:15:44,900 --> 00:15:49,940
♪I frown upon the fate
that brings us close but sets us apart♪

316
00:15:50,540 --> 00:15:53,860
♪Grieves well up♪

317
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:56,740
♪For this sad departure♪

318
00:15:57,580 --> 00:16:02,340
♪Love happens
before the destined separation♪

319
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:08,300
♪I resent that the blossom
cannot outlive the autumn♪

320
00:16:08,780 --> 00:16:14,460
♪I wish the scent still lingers
around your fingertip♪

321
00:16:14,830 --> 00:16:18,350
♪I ask not for a shared life with you♪

322
00:16:18,380 --> 00:16:21,380
♪But I yearn for a love♪

323
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:26,860
♪That carries on beyond time♪

324
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:33,700
♪A heart trapped in obsessions♪

325
00:16:34,180 --> 00:16:39,580
♪Shall break free at long last♪
